Description:
GMCM290921/01 - 311916166
As principal contractor you have failed to make available at readily accessible places, facilities such a sanitory conveniences, washing facilities and facilities for rest.

GMCM290921/02 - 311916472
The undertaking of your company is to install fibre optic cabling in the foot paths. The fences around the work are not in tact, clipped together and stable.  The excavated tracks are not fully covered by cover plates.  This has created a tripping risk to members of the public and home owners.
